item.title: CVE-2020-28400|2024-07-24T18:07:44.485Z -- siemens -- development%2Fevaluation%20kits%20for%20profinet%20io%3A%20dk%20standard%20ethernet%20controller
item.description: Affected devices contain a vulnerability that allows an unauthenticated attacker to trigger a denial-of-service condition. The vulnerability can be triggered if a large amount of DCP reset packets are sent to the device.
